data.description: Discover this beautiful Three Bedroom, Two Bath, Two Car Garage, CBS home with metal roof in Vero Lake Estates! You will lover the wide open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, large gourmet kitchen w/ breakfast bar and great room concept. Split floor plan with tile floors and large owner suite! Inside laundry room! Home is on county water and septic with low taxes! Private yard with screened porch and fenced yard!! Outstanding location that is convenient to area shopping, schools and I95!
